Absolutely delicious. It came out so juicy and tender. Trussing is very easy: there are many good videos on youtube showing you how to do it. I think the easiest truss is the figure-eight around the drumsticks. You really want to use a lot of salt and dry it really well. I think my skin would have been crispier if I dried it even more.

